
Flame pre-2025 user hotkey directory:  /opt/Autodesk/user/<username>/hotkey
Flame 2025 user shortcuts directory:  /path/to/your/home/dir/flame/shortcuts

How to use:

1.  cd /opt/Autodesk/user/<username>
2.  cp -r hotkey /var/tmp/hotkey_2024
3.  cp flame-hotkeys_convert.py /var/tmp/hotkey_2024/
4.  cd /var/tmp/hotkey_2024
5.  python flame-hotkeys_convert.py
6.  cp user.*.json /path/to/your/home/dir/flame/shortcuts/



